                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            A balanced diet is one that includes all food groups: carbohydrates, proteins, healthy fats,
                            vitamins,
                            and minerals to ensure that your body receives all the nutrients it needs.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq10">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
